verbose_text: Furthermore, some studies described that miR-1 inhibited the expression of MYLK3, CALM1, and CALM2 directly, which in turn led to down-regulation in the expression of CaM and CMLCK, followed by down-regulation of phosphorylation of MLC2v or CaMKIIdelta--cMyBP-C and impairment of contractile function [XREF_BIBR].
